
The Bathtub Experiment was performed on The Quad on May 18, 2007 from 1 p.m. sharp until 3 p.m. as a project piece for Professor Jon Rossinis Drama 159 Experimental Theatre class. Involved was a porcelain bathtub weighing 300 lbs. independently of the approximate 7580 gallons of water it held. Users/EliseKane conceived of and performed in the piece with her friend and classmate RebeccaGeorge.
